
---

**StreamQuiverMap**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes incoming data as a quiver of directional arrows, each representing rate and vector of change.

```markdown
# StreamQuiverMap - Directional Change Visualizer

StreamQuiverMap turns real-time numeric streams into animated arrows showing direction, strength, and flow.

## Features
- Real-time vector arrows  
- Dynamic rate mapping  
- Matplotlib animation

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamQuiverMap.git
cd StreamQuiverMap
python visualize.py
